WEBVTT

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:06.320
Learn WordPress gives you all the free educational resources you need to grow your skills, wherever

00:00:06.320 --> 00:00:09.720
you are on your WordPress journey.

00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:13.760
The new Learn WordPress site makes it easier for you to discover what you're interested

00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:22.000
in, browse featured courses, lessons, and online workshops.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:29.400
If you are ready to jump to a specific subject or level, it's only a search away.

00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:33.840
One of the most exciting new additions to the updated Learn WordPress experience is the

00:00:33.840 --> 00:00:36.500
introduction of Learning Pathways.

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:41.080
These are complete programs that let you improve your WordPress skills progressively.

00:00:41.080 --> 00:00:45.560
Learn the essentials of starting with WordPress or developing with WordPress, and then work

00:00:45.560 --> 00:00:50.280
your way through intermediate and advanced concepts at your own speed.

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:55.240
Each Learning Pathway is organized into modules or sections of lessons, which let you focus

00:00:55.240 --> 00:01:00.260
on building a solid foundation for your skills as you work through the course.

00:01:00.260 --> 00:01:07.560
In every course you'll find a mix of learning tools, video tutorials, text-based resources,

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:09.520
and quizzes.

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:15.400
On the homepage of a course or Learning Pathway, you can also access a private demo site to play

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:19.800
around and practice in, powered by WordPress Playground.

00:01:19.800 --> 00:01:23.460
You also have the option to register for a course.

00:01:23.460 --> 00:01:27.840
This lets you track your progress and save your place in a lesson if you need to come back to

00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:29.760
it later.

00:01:29.760 --> 00:01:33.720
You can also access most course content without registering.

00:01:33.720 --> 00:01:36.560
It's completely unlocked and available to anyone.

00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:41.900
So take a quick look to preview what you'll learn or share with a friend, client or colleague.

00:01:41.900 --> 00:01:47.320
There's always more to learn, so pick your path and learn your way.

00:01:47.320 --> 00:01:50.040
Get started at learn.wordpress.org